r />\nWiFi 開住幫到你定位<br />\n連智慧燈柱都知你走去邊"},{"pid":"08cdd4788ebe58d008a5bae7144315373c54e48c","tid":1801254,"uid":5733,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T04:21:52.000Z","msg":"沒得直接熄真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b891b56d5779f2332d661bf2954d8917f2d1919","tid":1801254,"uid":109923,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T05:38:59.000Z","msg":"冇得熄wifi最煩就係自動連，有時九巴路過都同我連巴士wifi<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次就係私隱問題，wifi都有定位作用<br />\n<br />\n啲人無腦洗地淨係識鳩叫wifi用好少電由得佢開住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ad73cbd959ace7382ae9a2c8995f3653aaacb9","tid":1801254,"uid":140303,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T05:48:49.000Z","msg":"雖然我好中意用apple 嘢但我覺得呢樣野真心on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我自己本身有無限數據 有時都會用下WIFI 但個問題係我轉返DATA 嘅時候 因為佢無幫我熄咗個WIFI 所以有時會自動連咗啲濕尻上唔到網嘅WIFI 之後再斷尻我DATA 我覺得呢樣野真心on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實點解唔可以long press 控制中心個wifi 之後有個掣係比用家真真正正咁熄咗個WIFI 佢？"},{"pid":"48319eb59b1a9c83a76d8641df23e056ef95c9cf","tid":1801254,"uid":66547,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"99c321506095db0af62ec9f0ecfd70842fe39d60","tid":1801254,"uid":64694,"like":1,"dislike":24,"score":-23,"quote":{"pid":"467ed2d52324157292560408b622a64f6229af03","tid":1801254,"uid":49151,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T13:20:33.000Z","msg":"唔洗閂冇意思"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T13:26:14.000Z","msg":"但我唔用WiFi嘅時候開著會唔會食電？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"唔用WiFi但用數據咪仲食電。<br />\n打開飛行模式咪可以息曬佢囉"},{"pid":"9909564755ce0ba31831d82a51f936a486592fd6","tid":1801254,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:39:29.000Z","msg":"有得SET防止自動連架，同埋佢唔想你關